Open file using WinRar (You can download WinRar at http://www.rarlab.com/) and extract the BSP file into
C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\<YOURUSER>\Counter-Strike: Source\CStrike\Maps

Then run Counter-Strike: Source and create your server, the map should now be in your map list, if not go to
the console and type in 'map de_dev_city' and the next time you run a server it should be in the map list.



Map was made by Chap1400, Any Custom Textures were made by Chris Chapman (And a special thanks to him!)

You can email me at: chap1410@googlemail.com

Thanks for downloading and enjoy!

Devious Methods is a Counter-Strike:Source defusal map set in an industrial storage facility. A team of terrorists has infiltrated the base, intent on disrupting their foreign enemies at any cost. A team of counter-terrorists has been dispatched to protect the facility and to eliminate the terrorist threat.

The map is built for teams of 5 or more. It easily supports 16+ players and encourages organized teamplay above other maps. The map is built in such a way that no matter where you are, you’re never safe from attack. Most locations in the map that give players an advantage over one location are vulnerable from another. This forces players to be vigilant, and to stick together to cover each other.

Gameplay is a mix of short- and long-range combat, though rifles seem to serve players better overall. There are plenty of sniper spots and flanking opportunities.

For comments or questions email cesig.moreis@gmail.com.  For more information and mapping discussion, visit http://blog.cizilux.com

Thanks, and have fun!

WHAT'S NEW IN VERSION 3:
- This version simply fixes the spawn point issues present in version 2. Sorry for the trouble.
* Removed malicious Terrorist spawn point from Front Yard.
* Now the map actually contains 64 working spawn points.

WHAT'S NEW SINCE VERSION 2:
- Contains bug fixes and a couple things to stop people from getting lost.
* Fixed exploits to gain access to roofs.
* Fixed the inability to crawl through bombsite B windows.
* Added lots of arrows pointing to bombsites.
* Named all the places of the map on the radar/nav mesh.
* Added 2 file cabinets near the double doors at mid to help CT's hold off T mid rush more effectively.
* Optimized some areas to slightly improve performance.

ORIGINAL FEATURES:
* Two (2) bomb sites (A & B)
* 64 spawn positions
* A few destructible doors & windows
* Full level overview
* Modified bot navigation file
* 3D sky box

TITLE: CS:S Map - de_desert_atrocity_v3
AUTHOR: SM Sith Lord
E-MAIL: smsithlord@yahoo.com
WEBSITE: http://www.engport.net

FILENAME: de_desert_atrocity_v3.bsp
FILESIZE: 18.7 MB (uncompressed)
DATE RELEASED: June 23rd, 2007

NOTES:
This map is intended for large games no smaller than 5v5. The nav mesh has been modified for bot use and radar place names.

CREDITS:
|NKM| Porkchop for play hosting the original beta. |DoP| Vulgar for play hosting version 1 and everybody at DoP High Times I server for actually playing it and finding bugs. Beta testers Beefcaike, Betty, N00b Vader, V1rus and dP Negs. 3v!L M!ke's reskin of the file cabinets.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
Put the bsp and nav in your maps folder.

STORY:
Invading forces have seized our beloved city and begun systematically looting it of all its prized possessions and religious treasures.

We cannot standby silently while these heathenistic trespassers desecrate our homeland and strip it of all its culture and righteous relics.

It is our father's will that we destroy these treasures and deliver them unto his hands rather than let them fall to these evil men.

This is not a battle to achieve victory, but rather a holy war waged to protect the integrity of your very own eternal soul.

Welcome death with the same passion that you wield it and your righteous glory shall be obtained!

Bomb Target A:
A house of worship located towards the western part of the city. The priceless treasures within this church have yet to be discovered by the occupying forces. Insure that these relics remain sacred, at all costs.

Bomb Target B:
The enemy has been stockpiling countless artifacts within the Great Tower until their relief can arrive to transport the treasures away. We must cause as much damage to the Great Tower as possible, but because of the occupation our access to the tower is greatly limited. Our best chance of saving the artifacts is bombing the mouth of the tower. Doing so will seal the tower shut and delay the evacuation of the loot. And this, our father willing, will cripple our enemies and insure your righteous glory in the everlasting.

ATTENTION: VERSION 3(III) OF THIS MAP IS READY FOR DOWNLOAD AT http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/27243 If you still wish to download the OLD VERSION of this map, continue reading below. ======================================= FEATURES: * Two (2) bomb sites (A & B) * 64 spawn positions * A few destructible doors & windows * Full level overview * Modified bot navigation file * 3D sky box NOTES: * No HDR lighting (to keep file size small) * Game Servers: The High Times DoP server has the map in rotation at 209.0.83.193:27015 Click here to see all servers that are currently on this map worldwide. Here is a very blurry YouTube video of gameplay and flythroughs. I'm working on finding a place to upload the HD WMV version of the video. #### Derelict Base - Bomb/Defuse

#####  By Will2k

de-derelict-base is a bomb/defuse map set in an ex-base and research facility that is left to decay. A group of terrorists is showing sudden interest in the abandoned facility. Intel suggests that an attack is
imminent at sunset to blast open the sealed doors.

The map is reminiscent of old-school deathmatch maps for Half-Life 1 and Opposing Force in regard to visual theme and general ambience. Those maps had great influence on me as a level designer some 12 years ago (the nostalgia :) especially "boot camp" and "lambda bunker". The Black Mesa inspiration can be seen throughout the map in several design aspects.

de-derelict-base features indoor locations as well as some outdoor areas. The gameplay is fast and distributed between narrow hallways and large tunnels and outdoor sections.


As usual, the map is fully optimized to ensure fluid gameplay and consistent high FPS.

The map has:

- 64 spawn points (32 vs 32) 
- radar overview
- Soundscapes
- Nav file with place names

For installation, simply extract the 4 files in the zip archive (bsp, nav and 2 txt files) to your \Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps folder.

I really hope you enjoy this map as much as I did creating it.
Comments and constructive feedback are always welcome.

Will2k

November 12, 2011
